<http://example.org/req/668#> a owl:Ontology .

<http://example.org/req/668#Req_0> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000031>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Thing,
        ns1:InformationContentEntity,
        ns1:RequirementSpecification ;
    rdfs:comment "From a point 1.6 m vertically from ground level, inside a 3 m horizontal radius from the TSAL c. In direct sunlight # EV.5.10 Connectors Tractive System connectors outside of a housing must meet one of the two: - Contain an Interlock EV.7.8 which must Open the Shutdown Circuit EV.7.2.2 - Be sealed at Tech Inspection IN.4.7.1 ## EV" ;
    ns1:requirementSatisfiedBy <http://example.org/req/668#DS_ObservationPoint>,
        <http://example.org/req/668#PS_ConnectorsCompliance>,
        <http://example.org/req/668#PS_InterlockOperation>,
        <http://example.org/req/668#PS_SealingAtInspection> .

<http://example.org/req/668#TSAL_c> a <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000001>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000002>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000004>,
        <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000040>,
        owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Thing .

